profile:
Instant Lawns is one of Ottawaâ€™s elite curb appeal experts specializing in re-sodding and new lawn installation. Our mission is to provide the most professional, convenient and efficient service the world of landscaping has ever seen. We are very proud to be one of Ottawa's lawn installation experts among the leaders of our industry. We have in place an ethos of extraordinary customer service. We swiftly answer you when you call or email us, are extremely reliable, always deliver what we promise you (on time AND on budget) and use only the best products and materials on every installation.

service_area: Instant Lawns provides Sod Installation, and landscaping services  in Ottawa from Dunrobin to Oreleans. We also provide Sodding services in the City of Ottawa and suburbs of Gloucester, Orleans, Blackburn Hamlet, Kanata, Nepean, Barrhaven, Bells Corners, Atla Vista/ Elmvale, Rockcliffe, Manor Park, New Edinburg, Riverside South, Findlay Creek, Carlingwood, Westboro, McKellar Park, Glebe, Greely, and Manotick.
